    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Ogre Chambers</strong> 是一款类Roguelike的弹幕射击游戏，你需要在不断变化的竞技场中抵御一波波怪物。如果你能坚持足够长时间，你将获得飞船升级奖励。你还可以保存多余的生命值，并在操作足够出色时将其转化为额外的升级。记得小心别被变化的墙壁压扁！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/f01867a06ed10d34c22154d7c2ba4979.poster.avif?t=1764017464\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/f01867a06ed10d34c22154d7c2ba4979.webm?t=1764017464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/f01867a06ed10d34c22154d7c2ba4979.mp4?t=1764017464\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>游戏特色：</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">7艘可解锁飞船</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">随机升级</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">可变换的竞技场</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">排行榜</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\">成就</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/a72b665c9bdc0db9292acad89bd4f842.poster.avif?t=1764017464\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/a72b665c9bdc0db9292acad89bd4f842.webm?t=1764017464\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2280440/extras/a72b665c9bdc0db9292acad89bd4f842.mp4?t=1764017464\" ty